[[Image:American Beaver.jpg|thumb|A beaver ({{senseno|en|rodent}})]]
From {{inh|en|enm|bever}}, from {{inh|en|ang|befer}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*bebru}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*bebruz}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*bʰébʰrus||beaver}}, derived from the root {{m|ine-pro|*bʰerH-||brown}}.

Cognate with {{cog|fy|bever}}, {{cog|nl|bever}}, {{cog|fr|bièvre}}, {{cog|de|Biber}}, dialectal {{cog|sv|bjur}}. Non-Germanic cognates include {{cog|cy|befer}}, {{cog|la|fiber}}, {{cog|lt|bẽbras}}, {{cog|ru|бобр}}, {{cog|ae|𐬠𐬀𐬎𐬎𐬭𐬀}}, and {{cog|sa|बभ्रु|tr=bábhru|t=mongoose; ichneumon}}. Related to {{m|en|brown}} and {{m|en|bear}}.

